criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  have confirmed medical diagnosis of type 2 DM;

          -  are 21 years old and above;

          -  have blood test result of HbA1c > 8% in the most recent test indicating poor glycemic
             control;

          -  possess and able to use smart mobile phone (e.g. Samsung Galaxy, iPhone) in their
             daily lives; and

          -  are able to speak and read English or Chinese.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  have suffered severe complications such as severe stroke, visual impairment, renal
             failure that interfere with self-care activities;

          -  have known history of major psychiatric illness;

          -  have reading and hearing difficulties.
